title: Rogue Legacy 1.0.13 [MAC] + EXTRAS
description:
Rogue Legacy 1.0.13 [MAC] + EXTRAS

Rogue Legacy Wineskin port for MAC. Just mount the .dmg and drag the app to your Applications folder. 
Extras included: artworks, avatars and wallpapers.

Patch included (1.0.13). To apply the last patch published by Cellar Door Games until now follow the next instructions:

Right click on the Rogue Legacy.app and choose Show Package Contents and double click the Wineskin.app.

Choose Install software, click Choose Setup Executable and navigate to the patch and click Choose.

Follow the screen prompts to install the update...when it's finished click close and your game should be fully updated.
